summary:
Motivated professional with 10 years of proven track record in education | customer service | administration | hotel management.
My strengths are high communication skills and solid administrative competences.
My customer oriented approach, empathy and ability to see the needs of the clients are a good asset to any company.
I’m purpose driven team player, proactive, able to work independently and prioritize.
Open for a challenging position in a friendly and goal oriented team.

Solution oriented 
Highly organized 
Able to prioritize and multitask 
Hands on mentality
Purpose driven
Flexible
Quick learner

Teaching/Tutoring
Interpretation
Translation 
Customer service
Office management
Hotel administration
